name: Julie Winter
text: Grabbed a Papa’s Favorite with modifications at this location on my way home from FW. It was almost closed so there wasn’t that much out and ready however their ingredients are always very fresh. …More

name: nick rich
text: Very delicious Pizza! All the employees were very helpful, especially the owner Justin. 10/10 would recommend to friends and family. Very clean and well maintained. Fantastic.

name: Leslie Vail
text: Staff is always fast and courteous. They always try to accommodate my weird requests.

name: Suzanne S
text: I saw the manager accidentally knock one of the pizza doughs on the floor and pick it up.  It was frustrating to watch all the employees tripping over themselves and the manager seemed to be absolutely clueless.  We love Papa Murphy's, but this location needs to get it together!

name: Marc Spinelli
text: Be nice if they could get my order right, but then again that might be asking to much.

name: trish smith
text: Lots of  toppings and ready to bake at home. I was so happy it was ready in 15 minutes and everyone loved it.

name: wayne
text: Loved this place, but it is no longer open.

name: Jessica Waters
text: Quick service and nice employees! Very clean too

name: Tyrone Reed
text: Super / Awesome Pizza and Outstanding Service.

name: Mark Taylor
text: Great pizza and service.

name: Rhys Brown
text: Tasty pizzas made to specs that can be bakes fresh at home.

name: Gabe Gentile
text: I saw Nick and Anthony Juuling in the back room.

name: JUDY GALLAGHER
text: Anthony was great :)

name: Allison Dixon
text: Great pizza, as usual.

name: Andrew Curtin
text: Horrible customer service, I was disrespected by Anthony and think he should be terminated immediately, he then proceeded to hit on my wife.

name: Laura Holubec
text: Amazing! Very nice people.

name: Rigg Bone
text: Cheap, big portions, quality ingredients

name: Justin Henninge
text: Huge pizza for the whole family. Make room in your fridge for left overs.

name: Jason Brown
text: Great take and bake pizzas!

name: Daniel Davis
text: The blonde lady that appears to be the boss doesn't seem to mind picking food up off the floor after dropping it and putting on your pizza ....gross
